import React from 'react'; var formatter = new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US',{ style: 'currency', currency: 'USD' }) const Coin = ( { id, symbol, name, image, current_price, market_cap, market_cap_rank, fully_diluted_valuation, total_volume, high_24, low_24, price_change_24h, price_change_percentage_24h, total_supply, max_supply, ath, ath_change_percentage, ath_date, last_updated } ) => { return (
{market_cap_rank}
{/*
*/}
{name}
{symbol.toUpperCase()}
{formatter.format(current_price)}
{formatter.format(price_change_24h)}
{price_change_percentage_24h.toFixed(2) + '%'}
{formatter.format(ath)}
{ath_change_percentage.toFixed(2) + '%'}
{formatter.format(market_cap)}
{last_updated}
) } export default Coin;
